HEADWORD: Ramayana
<hw>Ra*ma"ya*na</hw> <pr>(r⟦aum⟧*m⟦aum⟧"y⟦adot⟧*n⟦adot⟧)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Skr. <ets>R⟦amac⟧m⟦amac⟧ya⟦nsdot⟧a</ets>.]</ety>
